{"word":"ἀνθέριξ","slug":"ἀνθέριξ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνθέριξ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἄνθος,  ἀθήρ</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>the beard</i> of an ear of corn, <i>the ear</i> itself, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>spica</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>= <i>the stalk of asphodel</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}